name: EventMaster
0:
”Alexa, open Event Master”
”Alexa, ask Event Master what to do in Paris”
”Alexa, ask Event Master what events are in London tomorrow”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: event master
des: 'Event Master' is an Alexa skill able to search city events all around the world. Search the events specifying the city and the date you are interested about. 'Event Master' will retrieve the most popular events (using 'eventful' API, http://api.eventful.com/) and will list you the events information.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
